highlights.text: Mỹ Mỹ has the most spots on Viral Songs Vietnam. “'em sẽ cười tươi vào ngày anh cưới'” is the highest at #20.
“I Think I Like You Better When You’re Gone” by Reneé Rapp is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Vietnam at #40.
“愛人錯過” by 告五人 has been on Viral Songs Vietnam the longest, at 208 days straight.
“mây tan” by timtin is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Vietnam, up 34 spots at #50.
